acilities and equipment to meet customer demand, as well as capital improvements to and maintenance of existing facilities.  At", "bbox": [93.8, 963.8, 1144.4, 982.5]}, {"text": "FPL Energy, capital expenditures include, among other things, the cost, including capitalized interest, for construction of wind", "bbox": [93.8, 985.4, 1144.5, 1004.1]}, {"text": "projects and the procurement of nuclear fuel.  FPL FiberNet's capital expenditures primarily include costs to meet customer", "bbox": [93.8, 1007.0, 1144.4, 1025.8]}, {"text": "specific requirements and sustain its fiber-optic network.", "bbox": [93.8, 1028.6, 554.5, 1047.4]}]}